name: smartphone
description: A handheld device that combines mobile phone and computing functions.

name: tablet
description: A mobile device with a touchscreen display, larger than a smartphone.

name: smartwatch
description: A wearable device that offers smart features like notifications and health tracking.

name: headphones
description: A pair of speakers worn on or over the ears for listening to audio.

name: smart speaker
description: A wireless speaker with voice control capabilities.

name: gaming console
description: A device designed primarily for playing video games.

name: 4K TV
description: A television with a resolution of 3840 x 2160 pixels.

name: wireless mouse
description: A battery-operated pointing device that connects wirelessly to a computer.

name: external hard drive
description: A portable storage device used to store and back up data.

name: webcam
description: A camera that connects to a computer to stream video or take photos.

name: Bluetooth speaker
description: A portable speaker that connects to devices via Bluetooth for audio playback.

name: VR headset
description: A device worn on the head that provides immersive virtual reality experiences.

name: digital camera
description: A camera that captures photographs in digital format.

name: smart thermostat
description: A device that allows you to control your home's heating and cooling remotely.

name: robot vacuum
description: An autonomous vacuum cleaner that can navigate and clean floors on its own.
